    "The index improvement demonstrates that the AMRFB module can efficiently extract the features of low-light images while extending the receptive field.",
    "With the introduction of the Decouple Head module, the value of mAP@0.5 grew from 0.713 to 0.717, while the value of mAP@0.5:0.95 increased from 0.431 to 0.432.",
    "This module's requirement has been demonstrated.",
    "The index value was effectively enhanced once the SimSPPF module was introduced to replace the original SPPF module.",
    "The following trials convincingly demonstrate the necessity and usefulness of each module, as well as the superiority of our method."
